The paper focuses on the challenges faced by cybercrime investigators, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and cybercrime (cs.CY). The paper also discusses the practical, technical, and social issues faced by investigators, which could be relevant to human-computer interaction (cs.HC), social computing (cs.SI), and software engineering (cs.SE).
